## Results

Implemented a robust mic capture and Voice-to-Text pipeline. 
- Integrated real-time capture from mic via sounddevice
- RMS-based silence thresholding creates discrete chunks of speech vs quiet
- Converted chunks into WAV bytes in memory and passed successfully into Groq Whisper STT API
- Auto-rotating Groq whisper models (`whisper-large-v3`, `whisper-large-v3-turbo`) halves the rate limits
- Safely wires `stt.py` async transcripts straight to `main.py` -> `orchestrator.py` which triggers character LLM generations. 

